      <title>据《邮报》报道，津巴布韦储备支持 ZiG 升至 5.33 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/-zwg-usd-zimbabwe-reserves-backing-zig-rise-to-533-million-mail-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《星期日邮报》援引津巴布韦央行行长约翰·穆沙亚万胡的话报道，截至 1 月 9 日，受去年创纪录的黄金产量推动，津巴布韦支持 ZiG 的储备增至 5.33 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/-zwg-usd-zimbabwe-reserves-backing-zig-rise-to-533-million-mail-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 11:51:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
