      <title>冈比亚汇款与旅游业争夺外汇来源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/gambia-s-remittances-rival-tourism-as-source-of-foreign-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冈比亚央行行长表示，去年冈比亚收到的海外工人汇款大幅增加，已与旅游业媲美，成为该国经济的外汇来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/gambia-s-remittances-rival-tourism-as-source-of-foreign-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 10:17:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
