      <title>华尔街银行超越市场的反弹面临盈利考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/wall-street-banks-market-beating-rally-faces-earnings-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融集团（Jefferies Financial Group Inc.）的盈利初值令人失望，而就业报告又引发通胀担忧，华尔街银行今年的前景将备受关注。]]></description>
